OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1783878540
OL,3,CLinda Noskova battles back against
OL,4,CKarolina Muchova to win Wimbledon title
OL,6,FLinda Noskova put a dramatic second-
OL,7,Fset collapse behind her to win her
OL,8,Ffirst grand slam title in a wild
OL,9,FWimbledon final.
OL,11,FThe winner of the all-Czech clash
OL,12,Fbetween Noskova and Karolina Muchova
OL,13,Fwas guaranteed to be the third woman
OL,14,Ffrom the central European country to
OL,15,Flift the Venus Rosewater Dish in the
OL,16,Flast four years.
OL,18,F21-year-old Noskova, playing in her
OL,19,Ffirst grand slam final, impressively
OL,20,Fput the second set behind her to claim
OL,21,Fa 6-2 5-7 6-3 victory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
