OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1783878540
OL,3,CLinda Noskova battles back against
OL,4,CKarolina Muchova to win Wimbledon title
OL,6,FShe is the youngest women's champion
OL,7,Fsince another Czech, Petra Kvitova,
OL,8,Fwho was watching from the Royal Box,
OL,9,Fin 2011 and follows in the footsteps
OL,10,Fof 2023 champion Marketa Vondrousova
OL,11,Fand 2024 winner Barbora Krejcikova.
OL,13,F"It feels incredible," said Noskova
OL,14,Fafter being presented with the trophy
OL,15,Fby the Princess of Wales.
