OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1783878540
OL,3,CLinda Noskova battles back against
OL,4,CKarolina Muchova to win Wimbledon title
OL,6,F"All these matches have been so tough.
OL,7,FToday especially, it's never easy to
OL,8,Fget the last point. Karo, you really
OL,9,Fmade me work for it. We're friends.
OL,10,FI'm so glad that I could play my first
OL,11,Fgrand slam final with you. I think we
OL,12,Fmade history today."
OL,14,FNoskova was unable to hold back the
OL,15,Ftears as she paid tribute to her
OL,16,Fmother Ivana, who died from cancer two
OL,17,Fyears ago.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@TO]
