OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1783878540
OL,3,CLinda Noskova battles back against
OL,4,CKarolina Muchova to win Wimbledon title
OL,6,F"There's also one more person I would
OL,7,Flike to thank, which is my mum. I
OL,8,Fdefinitely would not be standing here
OL,9,Fwithout her so thank you," said
OL,10,FNoskova, blowing a kiss to the sky.
OL,12,FMuchova struggled to begin her
OL,13,Finterview through her own tears but
OL,14,Fpraised her young compatriot, saying:
OL,15,F"It's really tough to find any words.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@ZO]wD@AOU
