OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1783878540
OL,3,CLinda Noskova battles back against
OL,4,CKarolina Muchova to win Wimbledon title
OL,6,F"I'll start with Linda, my ex-friend.
OL,7,FI'm kidding, obviously ` kind of.
OL,8,FYou're so young and this was your
OL,9,Ffirst final of a grand slam and the
OL,10,Fway you handled it and the way you
OL,11,Fplayed, it was unbelievable."
OL,13,FFor just over an hour, this appeared
OL,14,Fto be one of Wimbledon's most
OL,15,Fstraightforward finals, with Noskova
OL,16,Fhandling her maiden major showpiece
OL,17,Fwith aplomb and dominating her more
OL,18,Fexperienced compatriot, who lost to
OL,19,FIga Swiatek in the French Open final
OL,20,Fin 2023.
