OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1783878540
OL,3,CLinda Noskova battles back against
OL,4,CKarolina Muchova to win Wimbledon title
OL,6,FLeading 6-2 5-2, Noskova was on the
OL,7,Fbrink, and Muchova had to scramble
OL,8,Fwith everything she had to force the
OL,9,Fninth seed to try to serve it out,
OL,10,Fsaving three match points as the crowd
OL,11,Fwilled a contest to break out.
OL,13,FBut then Noskova moved 30-0 ahead in
OL,14,Fthe next game and to within two points
OL,15,Fof victory, then a fourth chance
OL,16,Farrived and she double-faulted.
OL,18,FMuchova created an astonishing seven
OL,19,Fbreak points, three of which Noskova
OL,20,Fsaved with aces, before finally her
OL,21,Fresistance ran out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
