OL,3,CLinda Noskova battles back against
OL,4,CKarolina Muchova to win Wimbledon title
OL,6,FStill Noskova had the scoreboard
OL,7,Fpressure and a fifth match point
OL,8,Farrived in Muchova's next service game
OL,9,Fbut once again the 10th seed had the
OL,10,Fanswers and incredibly she made it
OL,11,Ffive games in a row to level the
OL,12,Fcontest.
