OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1783878540
OL,3,CLinda Noskova battles back against
OL,4,CKarolina Muchova to win Wimbledon title
OL,6,FNoskova headed back to her chair with
OL,7,Fher head in her hands before leaving
OL,8,Fthe court for the most important
OL,9,Fbathroom break of her career.
OL,11,FThe 21-year-old had showed impressive
OL,12,Fpoise all through her run, saving a
OL,13,Fmatch point of her own in the third
OL,14,Fround against Sorana Cirstea, and she
OL,15,Fknew how important the start of the
OL,16,Fdeciding set was.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
