PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1783878540
OL,3,CLinda Noskova battles back against
OL,4,CKarolina Muchova to win Wimbledon title
OL,6,FHad Muchova taken any of three break
OL,7,Fpoints in the opening game, the
OL,8,Foutcome might have been different, but
OL,9,FNoskova fought off the challenge to
OL,10,Fbreak the sequence of games against
OL,11,Fher and began to find her flowing
OL,12,Fshots again.
OL,14,FMuchova wowed the crowd with a between-
OL,15,Fthe-legs shot in the fifth game but
OL,16,FNoskova had the last laugh as she
OL,17,Fmoved, once again, into a 5-2 lead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
