PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1783878540
OL,3,CLinda Noskova battles back against
OL,4,CKarolina Muchova to win Wimbledon title
OL,6,FNoskova is not your average 21-year-
OL,7,Fold tennis player. A passionate
OL,8,Fenvironmentalist, she spent part of
OL,9,Fher off-season last year volunteering
OL,10,Fat a school in Tanzania, keeping her
OL,11,Fprofession a secret.
OL,13,FMaybe such worldly perspective helped,
OL,14,Ffor this time she did not blink,
OL,15,Fsending down an ace to bring up a
OL,16,Fsixth match point and this time taking
OL,17,Fit thanks to another unreturnable
OL,18,Fserve before collapsing to the court
OL,19,Fin triumph ` and relief.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
